<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Lilcrunch</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-01-17 09:42:39</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Dark Bone Bracelet in unrest was not that bad to get.  Just shout in the zone and many people will let you loot it.<BR>
<BR>
The Griffene charm on the other hand, took three weeks to get.  I was in on parties killing at least 100 griffennes with no charm.  I finally offered 20pp to loot one over shout and it still took four hours before one dropped. <BR>
<BR>
Lambent stones can be easily purchased from players for around 50pp.  Just remember, you will need to bring 1100 GOLD pieces with you to the temple for the gems.  They are 550 gold each.  Don't do it with plat, you'll lose it.<BR>
<BR>
Lilcrunch<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
