<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>The fire opals can indeed be purchased with 55 plat, no problem.  Both drops seem fairly rare (dark boned skull drops more frequently than dark boned bracelet; griffenne feather drops more frequently than griffenne charm).  However, the quest is still fairly easy, and can be done at low level with friends or benevolent people in the zone.</font></td></tr></table>
